            <title>[HIVE-6039] Round, AVG and SUM functions reject char/varch input while accepting string input</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-6039</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;An error similar to the following will occur:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;hive&amp;gt; create table tabs (c &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;char&lt;/span&gt;(8), vc varchar(10)) ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;\t&apos;&lt;/span&gt;;
hive&amp;gt; select sum(c), avg(c), sum(vc), avg(vc) from tabs;
FAILED: UDFArgumentTypeException Only numeric or string type arguments are accepted but &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;char&lt;/span&gt;(8) is passed.
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
